OL,3,CMan dies and woman remains in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after A703 crash
OL,6,FA man has died following a fatal crash
OL,7,Fon the A703 between Eddleston and
OL,8,FLeadburn.
OL,10,FThe incident happened around 3:05pm on
OL,11,F26 February 2024, involving a grey
OL,12,FNissan Note and a white Ford Kuga.
OL,14,FEmergency services attended and the 86-
OL,15,Fyear-old male passenger of the Nissan
OL,16,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,18,FThe 82-year-old female driver was
OL,19,Ftaken to the Royal Infirmary of
OL,20,FEdinburgh where she remains in a
OL,21,Fcritical condition.
