OL,6,FThe driver of the Ford, a 40-year-old
OL,7,Fman, was also taken to the Royal
OL,8,FInfirmary of Edinburgh for treatment
OL,9,Fand has since been released.
OL,11,FThe road was closed while
OL,12,Finvestigations were carried out and
OL,13,Freopened around 9pm.
OL,15,FSergeant Barry Sommerville of Lothians
OL,16,Fand Borders Road Policing said: "Our
OL,17,Fthoughts are with the family and
OL,18,Ffriends of the man who died, and our
OL,19,Fenquiries are ongoing to establish the
OL,20,Ffull circumstances.
